Bangun!

700
01:43:38,580 --> 01:43:39,714
Jangan tidur!

701
01:43:41,015 --> 01:43:43,718
Paman, bangun! Jangan mati!

702
01:44:20,254 --> 01:44:21,456
Mirai...

703
01:44:24,025 --> 01:44:25,627
Aku harus pulang.

704
01:44:29,631 --> 01:44:31,633
Aku harus kembali
kepada istri dan putriku.

705
01:44:42,944 --> 01:44:44,579
Hei... Sampai jumpa.

706
01:44:57,725 --> 01:44:59,126
Mirai...

707
01:45:07,101 --> 01:45:08,636
Ayah!

708
01:45:08,670 --> 01:45:10,237
- Paman.
- Ayah!

709
01:45:14,642 --> 01:45:15,743
Ayah!

710
01:46:05,527 --> 01:46:08,863
<i>Kami telah membongkar</i>
<i>seluruh jaringan perdagangan manusia itu.</i>

711
01:46:08,896 --> 01:46:10,865
<i>Aku bahkan masih</i>
<i>tidak tahu namamu.</i>

712
01:46:10,898 --> 01:46:13,735
Temanku yang misterius.

713
01:46:29,917 --> 01:46:32,086
Wang

714
01:46:36,724 --> 01:46:38,325
Wei

715
01:46:43,164 --> 01:46:45,066
Hmm.

716
01:47:01,382 --> 01:47:03,785
<i>Jika kau cukup berani</i>
<i>untuk mengubah dirimu sendiri...</i>

717
01:47:04,619 --> 01:47:06,053
<i>kau bisa mengubah dunia.</i>

718
01:47:06,688 --> 01:47:07,889
<i>Wang Wei.</i>

719
01:47:22,704 --> 01:47:24,572
Kau sangat cantik.

720
01:47:31,145 --> 01:47:32,146
Ayah.

721
01:47:33,881 --> 01:47:35,783
Maukah kau menceritakan
kisahmu sekarang?

722
01:47:52,967 --> 01:47:54,736
Saat pertama kali aku bertemu ibumu...

723
01:47:57,145 --> 01:48:03,889
Diterjemahkan oleh Lee Jin